name: THE BWSTREET - A Tribute to Bwople
description:
My interpretation of the BWOPLE project created by @gengoya_club . Also a submission for the #BwopleArtEvent. An event initiated by the creator and @mondayartclub.

For me, who is quite lazy to think about the combination of color schemes, this event really makes me happy.
